          <li class="lol"><b>2015</b> - became co-chair of OpenAI, a non-profit aiming to advance digital intelligence to benefit humanity.</li>
          <li class="lol"><b>2017</b>-Tesla announced that it surpassed General Motors to become the most valuable U.S. car maker. Musk was backing a venture called Neuralink, which intends to create devices to be implanted in the human brain and help people merge with software.</li>
